						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment of 113 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold to the temple of Tiruvīśalūr Perumānaḍigaḷ, left in charge of the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of Nālūr, by <hi rend="bold">Śembiyaṉ Kāraikkāḍuḍaiyāṉ</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Aṉṉiyūraḍigaḷ</hi> for feeding a person daily in the temple with the monthly interest of a <hi rend="italic">kuṉṟi</hi> on each <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of the amount.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
